== Ibinyoro ==
'''Ibinyoro''' n'indwara y'ibasira Ikiremwa muntu, Igafata cyane uruhu, amagufwa n'utundi duce, nka [[Itabi|karitiraje]], ibinyoro akaba n'indwara yandura hagati y'umuntu n'undi, ikaba yarabayeho kuva kera<ref>https://ubuzimainfo.rw/byinshi-ku-ndwara-yibinyoro-indwara-itera-kwangirika-ku-ruhu-iyo-itavuwe-kare/</ref>. 

== Uko indwara y'ibinyoro yandura ==
Ubusanzwe indwara y'ibinyoro n'indwara utera Kwangirika kuruhu iyo itavuwe kare. Indwara y'ibinyoro ikaba iterwa n'agakoko ka [[Itabi|peretonema]] [[Itabi|peretenuwa]]. Indwara y ibinyoro ikaba ikunda kuboneka mugihugu cyangwa mubice aho isuku arinke, nanone ibinyoro bikunda kuboneka mubice by'amashyamba, ikaba iterwa n'isuku nkeya<ref>https://umutihealth.com/betamethasone/</ref>. 




